<h2>Importance of Learning JavaScript</h2>
<p>JavaScript, along with HTML and CSS, is one of the 3 crucial languages all web developers must learn. These languages allow you to manage the content, layout, and behavior of web pages.</p>

<h3>Versions Covered</h3>
<p>This guide includes every version of JavaScript, starting from the original JavaScript ES1, ES2, ES3 (1997-1999), the first major revision ES5 (2009) and ongoing yearly updates.</p>

<h2>Manage Your Pace of Learning</h2>
<p>You control the pace of your learning in this tutorial. Take a break or revisit the content if you're finding it difficult. Practicing and coding will help you become an adept programmer.</p>

